dct_title_s: Map showing Existing Conditions, Present U.S. Pierhead and Bulkhead Line, Old Riparian Line & Construction of New Bulkhead. Also Old Line of Wharf now removed
dct_description_sm: Case 1970: Shows pierhead & bulkhead line May 22, 1916, old riparian line of 1877, exterior line of wharf removed, bulkhead under construction, and Mulroy-Cook property.
